1.Student:
As a user, i want to use a website which have accurate data and information of world population so that i can use that for my university research paper.

2.Journalist:
As a user, i want to use such a website which is easy to navigate so that i can save time to do my project.

3.Data entry Manager:
As a data entry manager, i want to modify data and information which is saved in the website so that website is up to date.

4.Administrator:
As an admin, i want to manage incoming and outgoing correspondence so that the website is runnable.

5.Colleague:
As an internal user of the website, i would like to be guided through the platforms so that i can discover all the features. 
